{
  "stem": "27507.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a writer and he was a doctor and he was an educationalist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wrote books in a whole series of books for children mainly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of the-- and he had as well-- he was appearing in Polish radio, but that was before the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had-- and I remember some of those-- the books were-- there was a book about Polish children and there was a book about-- I remember the names of those books.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was book called [POLISH] Polish names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was another book called [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] something like [POLISH] in other words, Jewish names.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[POLISH], it was Moses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [POLISH] was a small nickname of coming from Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and-- so that would-- because he had, of course, an orphanage for Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course he was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course he was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Janusz Korczak was his-- was his-- pseudonym.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But his real name was Henryk Goldszmit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course he was Jewish and the orphanage was Jewish and all- most of the staff or all of the staff in orphanage was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the orphanage existed for many years before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and Korczak had his own educational principles, which were basically principles that children have to be allowed to develop according to their natural principles, that children are naturally good, that one has to encourage in children their instincts of justice and fairness and so on.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was -- Korczak was famous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During the war, I think they had great problems with supplies, with food, but they managed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think Korczak was so well-known that he had all kinds of people who were helping.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were as well doing all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Among other things they had this theater, where there was a marionette theater.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
